text: Sugar Fields () is a 2016 Dominican Republic drama film directed by Fernando Baez Mella. It was selected as the Dominican entry for the Best Foreign Language Film at the 89th Academy Awards but it was not nominated. ==Cast== * Héctor Aníbal as Samuel ==See also== * List of submissions to the 89th Academy Awards for Best Foreign Language Film * List of Dominican submissions for the Academy Award for Best Foreign Language Film ==References== ==External links== * Category:2016 films Category:2016 drama films Category:Dominican Republic films Category:Spanish-language films
